Boost: 
1. download boost 1.55.0
2. cd boost_1.55.0/tools/build/v2
3. bootstrap.sh 
4. cd boost_1.55.0
5. ./b2 --prefix=<destination path> threading=single (threading=single may be
removed)

Boost:
1. download boost 1.56.0
2. cd boost_1.56.0/
3. bootstrap.sh 
4. ./b2 --prefix=<destination path> 

Xcerces
1. download xerces-c-3.1.1
2. unzip xerces to msys64 and get into the path xerces-c-3.1.1
3. run ./configure CFLAGS=-O3 CXXFLAGS=-O3 --prefix=<the path you want to save
the include and lib of xerces> --disable-sse2 (--disable-sse2 may be removed).
4. enter src and run make clean make

Xalan
1. export XERCESCROOT=<path>/proteomics_cpp/thirdparty/xerces-c-3.1.1/
2. export XALANCROOT=<path>/proteomics_cpp/thirdparty/xalan-c-1.11/c/
3. ./runConfigure 
4. edit src/xalanc/Makefile 
5. edit src/xalanc/Utils/XalanMsgLib/Makefile. 
6. see the Makefile in the directory
7. make 
8. make install

Htslib
1. cd htslib
2. make

Download links:
1. boost 1.55.0 (boost_1_55_0.zip): http://sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/boost/1.55.0/
2. xerces-c-3.1.1 (xerces-c-3.1.1.zip): http://xerces.apache.org/xerces-c/download.cgi
3. xalan 1.11 (xalan_c-1.11-src.zip): http://xalan.apache.org/xalan-c/download.html
4. htslib: https://github.com/samtools/htslib
